#: ../../Entrance_Tank.rst:10
msgid ""
"Design information for the AguaClara entrance tank is available in `the "
"Entrance Tank Design chapter of The Physics of Water Treatment Design "
"<https://aguaclara.github.io/Textbook/Flow_Control_and_Measurement/ET_Design.html>`_."
msgstr ""

